episode_summary: Ryan Young shares his journey from a professional chef to leading Ohio's top real estate team. He emphasizes the importance of discipline and work ethic learned from the culinary world. Ryan introduces Fellow, a tool designed to convert existing database contacts into seller leads, offering a unique approach to lead generation.
